{"tid":1104563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"同唔熟嘅人飲茶真係好尷尬","createTime":"2019-04-13T08:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T09:56:56.000Z","uid":199292,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3201d9d15a94bc50cb1ae783c6ab1e671fe42450","tid":1104563,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:32:27.000Z","msg":"由坐低浪碗杯筷子 叫嘢食<br />\n去到夾嘢食大家都扮晒禮讓<br />\n講咗自己嚟人地係都要幫你斟茶夾嘢 跟手又要幫返人<br />\n又驚自己同人習慣唔一樣比人覺得冇禮貌點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想食餐飽下下都要就住就住<br />\n<br />\n想快啲走 好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c83e481bd55a901f5e8dc250c703456ed22611","tid":1104563,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"反檯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90ce49794e88ed14cdfadb8ef3ff3dd88e78593","tid":1104563,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"比錢先係boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7126e9f46037fbfd822e5ebff4f84a9e18b67c84","tid":1104563,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"有無嗌灌湯餃"},{"pid":"874d1065fd7b7e3031a36eadd887b89260b23210","tid":1104563,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"最撚麻煩係要用公筷，大家扮晒衛生"},{"pid":"da431ee0af35a47892153e903d3f205925e91295","tid":1104563,"uid":17425,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"係 好撚怕，想叫d 貴少少既都要就住 但只係蝦餃小籠包<br />\n<br />\n蝦餃又話唔值<br />\n牛柏葉就漂白水<br />\n牛肉就大陸牛 <br />\n叫蒸飯又話飲茶緊係食點心，食蒸飯係窮人先咁食<br />\n心諗不如你唔好黎飲茶啦，想食乜咪食乜。<br />\n<br />\n利申 同呢個人飲左一次之後無下次"}]}